# Xcode / Swift — track system.
# (The repo-root .gitignore already covers `build/` and `.DS_Store`.)

## Xcode per-user state (never shared)
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

## Derived data / build output
build/
DerivedData/
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.dSYM
*.dSYM.zip
*.ipa

## Swift Package Manager (when track adds packages)
.build/
.swiftpm/
